{
  "texts": [
    "The successful implementation of deep learning models, particularly convolutional neural networks (CNNs), has been demonstrated in various CV applications in recent years.",
    "These applications include traffic detection (Yang et al. 2019a, b), recognition of medical images (Sundararajan et al. 2019), text identification (Melnyk et al. 2019), facial recognition (Kumar and Singh 2020), and crop yield predictions (Damos 2015), etc.",
    "Many deep learning-based methods have recently been used in agriculture to detect plant diseases and pests.",
    "Many domestic and international companies have built WeChat applets and object/disease identification apps.",
    "Additionally, it is made simpler and less expensive by automated disease diagnosis that requires the observation of symptoms on plant leaves."
  ]
}